  "body": "When blocking / unblocking a user, which has custom userpic, the appearance of the picture is not consistent.\r\n\r\nCase 1, user is not blocked: custom pic is shown on chat tab, user's profile, 1x1 chat header\r\nCase 2, user is blocked: custom pic is shown on chat tab, user's profile, **not shown** in 1x1 chat header\r\nCase 3: user is unblocked: custom pic is shown on chat tab, user's profile, **not shown** in 1x1 chat header\r\n\r\nWe need to agree on what to expect when blocking user in terms of displaying its custom pic. To me it looks like we just lose the picture in 1x1 chat and it needs to be fixed.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1552\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-09-08 at 12 39 01\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/132497718-cb429490-42ef-4875-ac8b-7f5aec6b3d01.png\">\r\n",
